All the lively, happy birds are singing chirp, chirp, chirp<br />
All the west winds happily play catch<br />
All the anemones paint the meadows in white, white, white<br />
All the girls are trying out their new hats</p>
<p>All the boys are happy that the woolen socks<br />
Are changed to light nylon by the girls</p>
<p>April, it doesn&#8217;t matter if the winter&#8217;s been hard<br />
April, when you can let your blonde hair down now</p>
